BEGIN:VEVENT
BEGIN:2025-12-03 04:00:00+00:00
DESCRIPTION:Rome Années 80\, Goliarda Sapienza travaille depuis dix ans s
 ur ce qui sera son chef-d'œuvre "L'Art de la joie". Mais son manuscrit es
 t rejeté par toutes les maisons d'édition. Désespérée\, Sapienza comm
 et un vol qui lui coûte sa réputation et sa position sociale. Incarcér
 ée dans la plus grande prison pour femmes d'Italie\, elle va y rencontrer
  des voleuses\, des junkies\, des prostituées mais aussi des prisonnière
 s politiques. Après sa libération\, elle continue à rencontrer ces femm
 es et développe avec l'une d'entre elles une relation qui lui redonnera l
 e désir de vivre et d'écrire.
END:2025-12-03 04:00:00+00:00
NAME:Fuori
URL:https://www.pathe.ch/fr/films-evenements/fuori-47288
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
BEGIN:2026-04-09 04:00:00+00:00
DESCRIPTION:Mike is stuck in limbo. Literally. Mike is a ghost. Equipped w
 ith a healthy dose of cynicism\, he seems to have accepted his fate in the
  in-between world-until\, during one of his mischievous little stunts in t
 he cinema that no one ever notices\, he is reprimanded by a girl. Elli can
  see and hear him\, and she is thoroughly annoyed. His attempts to explain
  that he is a ghost do not make things any easier. Reluctantly\, she engag
 es with him\, and a friendship emerges perfect for an introverted teenager
  like Elli. Mike becomes her imaginary friend\, understanding her loneline
 ss and sadness in a way no one in Elli's life has since her father passed 
 away. But a ghost must eventually take the final journey\, and a teenager 
 must grow up. Fate has not brought them together by chance.
END:2026-04-09 04:00:00+00:00
NAME:Ghost Bastard
URL:https://www.pathe.ch/fr/films-evenements/ghost-bastard-51784
END:VEVENT
